<br>
Here is our situation. Due to recent disagreements among the officers who formed the guild, there has been a split which led to a number of members leaving. What we have currently is a group of about 7 people who make it a point to show up for planned raids and stay until the end, about 7 people who show up for raids if they happen to be online at the time, about 7 people who probably will begin to show up for raids if we ever get things off the ground again, but who will leave if we don't show any improvement over the next few weeks, and about 50 members who will never show up for anything. <br>
<br>
Now, hehe, I realize that doesnt sound very appealing in an alliance partner. Hear me out, though. <br>
<br>
What we are looking for is a guild in a similar boat, who has a core set of people who would like to do raids appropriate for levels 50-60 but who are not strong enough on their own to do them.. a guild who could add their 7 strong 50-60 level members to our 7 strong 50-60 level members, and by having just this wee bit of added force, be able to accomplish things we can neither one of us do alone. We are aware that we at this time do not represent a strong force and we are not seeking an alliance with someone who clearly outpowers us, who we might seem to be more of a burden or annoyance to, and who would in all reality simply absorb us. Its is our hope that we can find a guild who is also struggling on the cusp of being a good force, a guild who is also facing the issue of trying to keep the very reliable core of people from going insane with boredom due to lack of participation from the rest of the guild. A guild who currently has difficulty recruiting and keeping higher level members due to lack of raiding opportunity. A guild who has aspirations to grow stronger along with us, and who is patient enough to take small steps toward higher goals. <br>
<br>
What we do not need is more people who cannot be relied upon. In other words, we would much rather have an alliance with a guild who could absolutely provide 5 good people for every raid, than an alliance with someone who might be able to provide 15 good people for a raid once in a while. <br>
<br>
If you represent a guild such as I have described, and you wish to talk about an alliance with us, please send a tell to me (as Helianthus, Oxalis, or Begonia), to Munu/Ssterling, or to our guildleader (Justanote). Note and I are on every night, Munu takes the day shift. <br>
